node.text: @capsulebyjuliette Yes.. its been rather one great time to reconnect and get our acts together. Cant say that for others marginal classes though. They have suffered the most

During the circuit-breaker, I managed to keep my daily exercise routine at home, yoga or pilates, thanks to the great app #AloMoves. It is more essential than ever, every morning, to keep my body and mind balanced! Especially when you know that you will have a few hours of kids home learning...followed by your own work! Keep on breathing 💨
What has your personal practice looked like lately?
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
🇫🇷 Chaque jour, ma routine inclue 1h de yoga ou de pilates. Pendant le confinement j’ai pu garder cette routine chaque matin grâce à l’app #AloMoves, plus essentielle que jamais afin de garder mon équilibre physique et mental! Surtout en sachant que quelques heures d’école à la maison m’attendent...puis mon propre travail! On respire 💨
Et vous, à quoi ressemble votre pratique physique ces derniers temps?
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
